、年輕人也好，他們如果想到台灣讀書或就業，台灣都會提供必要的協助，現階段還不需要《難民法》。<br />\n<br />\n《港澳條例》第18條規定，「對於因政治因素而致安全及自由受有緊急危害之香港或澳門居民，得提供必要之援助」。"},{"pid":"3c02bd383e1918e252870e724b66194556c1e6b5","tid":1772531,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"宜家台灣爆出KMT奶共集體賣台仲有拉咗果件向心就係統戰部五毛呀頭<br />\n大家都一樣受共匪入侵好應該兄弟努力不撤不割樓豬就出post搞分化到底有乜居心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816ccb61db7c31112c971d7021c92cc9b35dfc82","tid":1772531,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"唔緊要 , 至緊要共產黨輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e955e87596030ae7089a5e33b7bb909d62664","tid":1772531,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"咁又點? 依家玩道德潔癖呀?<br />\n第一日先知"},{"pid":"1e022741de874372a61c85f58e2fde9b2c0675b8","tid":1772531,"uid":103050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"on9五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣人好好抗共就係對香港人最大既支持"},{"pid":"fcdacb0071e3a60c3f536193a757c437a5a10372","tid":1772531,"uid":211196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a186420bcf407c6bdbb73702358273dff58f476f","tid":1772531,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"6ecc1aa7735eb1614a63924ac2b6efd899d24ea9","tid":1772531,"uid":42580,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又係呢個分化五毛撚 請善用起底功能 分化完澳門又分台灣</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"其實你知唔知咩叫分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\